N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4108.1 - Eligibility

State Regulations

For purposes of eligibility, a racing season or racing
year shall be the calendar year. In recording winnings, gross winnings will be
used and odd cents will be dropped and disregarded. Notes
